{"tid":1265214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[7.1遊行]香港人堅持！一個月都未有點可以放棄！要明白改變從來唔係一時三刻做到嘅事","createTime":"2019-06-29T05:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T06:47:45.000Z","uid":139474,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c03edc335651d7b173970865cfb3e6244e789caf","tid":1265214,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:40:15.000Z","msg":"有人說，香港人正落後零比五。<br />\n<br />\n或許是史上最漫長的六月，捱過催淚彈如雨下、橡膠子彈瞄準頭部發射的血腥長日，頭盔、雨傘、彈殼散落一地。面對濫權濫暴，甚至被指是暴徒，港人筋竭力疲。<br />\n<br />\n2016年十月，韓國時任總統朴槿惠被揭發干政醜聞，污點越揭越多，引起全國憤怒。<span style=\"color: red;\">23個星期集會，逾1,500萬人次參與，國民堅持燭光集會抗爭長達半年，</span>要求朴槿惠下台。2017年三月，法官全票通過彈劾裁決，朴槿惠<span style=\"color: red;\">即時被罷免</span>。<br />\n<br />\n2018年十一月，法國「黃背心運動」全國遍地開花，<span style=\"color: red;\">民眾每周末到不同地點示威表達訴求，高峰期一日逾30萬人參與。</span>政府其後數日間先後宣佈暫緩及擱置提高燃油稅，今年四月宣佈一系列減稅、改革措施。當地警方曾出動催淚彈、水炮、橡膠子彈、防暴手榴彈等武器驅趕，法國內政部已成立專家小組檢討警方鎮壓手法。示<span style=\"color: red;\">威行動持續至今逾30周</span>。<br />\n<br />\n港人高喊「反送中」，由三月1萬人，四月13萬人，六月100萬人，到創造歷史的200萬零1人。現實叫人氣餒，但港人從未放棄，有人站在前線無畏無懼，有人站在後方不離不棄。灰心、失望理所當然，休息過後，「三罷」、一浪浪不合作、圍堵運動湧至。眾籌在全球報章刊登廣告，半日之內已超額籌得670萬元，誓要國際社會聽得見港人呼聲。不是天降奇迹，就是我們擇善固執。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">「當你覺得好辛苦嘅時候，其實都仲有人會撐住你，唔係得你自己一個。」<br />\n<br />\n不認命，堅守信念，我們從不孤單。七一，香港人，繼續街頭見。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">七一遊行2019<br />\n主題：撤回惡法 林鄭下台<br />\n副題/口號：重啟政改 釋放所有政治犯 撤銷暴動定性 徹查612鎮壓<br />\n日期：2019年7月1日<br />\n集合時間：下午2時30分<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣維園中央草坪至金鐘政府總部<br />\n主辦團體：民間人權陣線</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190629/59768008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190629%2F59768008&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmq3GrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=12b7fdb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190629%2F59768008&h=ab16b277\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190629/59768008</a>"},{"pid":"a8e1b5b1e3f8778978082a2147e1c161186f5e14","tid":1265214,"uid":79024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:01:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ccc82672d0e915ecac97598bcccfc632f87f644","tid":1265214,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:41:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193554ee2cf61838f78157fc2bdcee60051d183e","tid":1265214,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:41:31.000Z","msg":"睇完幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975f97199ea66d5cfdbe6d5de6b58c4bf1d3c55d","tid":1265214,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2259ee8391573fda0a30b98749ef61b6691e55","tid":1265214,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:41:52.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93ae43e9d9392095bca5ca5e141106920215344","tid":1265214,"uid":46093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:43:03.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739beb63366b0b614bfd099f0bbc779c5785ab4f","tid":1265214,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:43:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">七一野餐會 <br />\n人數決定一切</span></span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;  唔 理 衝 唔 衝 ， 迫 爆 金 紫 荊 &mdash;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1265048\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1265048</a><br />\n<br />\n【七一升級&middot;屌爆升旗禮】不舉係近來對政府施壓最重大嘅機會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1264575\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1264575</a><br />\n<br />\n71 香港不舉行動 計劃大綱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1263717\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1263717</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">裝備及戰術POST！</span><br />\n<br />\n[同我推晒佢] 力抗膠post 621行動討論整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242813\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242813</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">記得帶gear啦，迫爆至上，人數決定一切</span>"},{"pid":"eaa688cfdd745f565b205ba6be014abdce583236","tid":1265214,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:47:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f3254ada568e831fcd7de35cef9d980369dfe3","tid":1265214,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:47:45.000Z","msg":"大家7月1見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}